  <ul id="superfish-1" class="menu sf-menu sf-menu-primary-nav-menu sf-navbar sf-style-none sf-total-items-3 sf-parent-items-3 sf-single-items-0"><li id="menu-28611-1" class="first odd sf-item-1 sf-depth-1 sf-total-children-2 sf-parent-children-0 sf-single-children-2 menuparent"><span>Key <br />Issues</span><ul><li id="menu-28691-1" class="first odd sf-item-1 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="../../animal-homelessness.html" title="" class="sf-depth-2">Animal Homelessness</a></li><li id="menu-30656-1" class="last even sf-item-2 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="../../animal-cruelty.html" title="" class="sf-depth-2">Animal Cruelty</a></li></ul></li><li id="menu-28626-1" class="middle even sf-item-2 sf-depth-1 sf-total-children-3 sf-parent-children-0 sf-single-children-3 menuparent"><span>Our <br />Response</span><ul><li id="menu-30661-1" class="first odd sf-item-1 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="../../animal-rescue.html" title="" class="sf-depth-2">Animal Rescue</a></li><li id="menu-30666-1" class="middle even sf-item-2 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="../../animal-placement.html" title="" class="sf-depth-2">Animal Placement</a></li><li id="menu-30671-1" class="last odd sf-item-3 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="../../animal-protection.html" title="" class="sf-depth-2">Animal Protection</a></li></ul></li><li id="menu-28606-1" class="last odd sf-item-3 sf-depth-1 sf-total-children-4 sf-parent-children-0 sf-single-children-4 menuparent"><span>How You <br />Can Help</span><ul><li id="menu-30676-1" class="first odd sf-item-1 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="../../ways-to-give.html" title="" class="sf-depth-2">Ways to Give</a></li><li id="menu-28661-1" class="middle even sf-item-2 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="../../team-aspca.html" title="" class="sf-depth-2">Fundraise with Team ASPCA</a></li><li id="menu-28676-1" class="middle odd sf-item-3 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="../../take-action.html" title="" class="sf-depth-2">Take Action</a></li><li id="menu-28671-1" class="last even sf-item-4 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="../../adopt-pet.html" title="" class="sf-depth-2">Adopt a Pet</a></li></ul></li></ul>
